text: Attila Racz (born 15 June 1973) is a Romanian rower. He competed in the men's coxless pair event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Romania Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
